•   credit.p.(q+1)

=   Theory [5]

    pz.p.(n+1) - bz.p.(n+1)

=   Theory [6,7]

    (pz.p.q + [a.q ≥ 0]) - (bz.p.q + [a.q < 0])

=   Arithmetic

    pz.p.q + [a.q ≥ 0] - bz.p.q - [a.q < 0]

=   Arithmetic

    pz.p.q - bz.p.q + [a.q ≥ 0] - [a.q < 0]

=   Definition of credit

    credit.p.q + [a.q ≥ 0] - [a.q < 0]

